Package entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Creates an Admin object.
    App
    An App object stores the details of an application as listed in the system.
    AppUsage
    AppUsage records the details of an application and its usage details.
    DiurnalAppUsage
    DiurnalAppUsage records the details of diurnal pattern report usage details.
    TopkUsage
    TopkUsage records the details of Top-k usage details.
    TopkUsageResult
    TopkUsageResult records the details of Top-k usage result details.
    User
    User represents a user of the system, and stores all the details of a user/student.
    UserAppUsage
    UserAppUsage tracks a user's details and application usage by storing a list of app usage time stamps as well as the corresponding app categories of all the applications used.
